{"type": "article", "id": 22573, "title": "不是我不明白，这世界变化快 |好奇心研究所", "description": "有时候起晚了，一刷朋友圈就有种 out 的感觉。", "date": "2016-02-21T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021206063UdPYh1ulniIqpmC.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 还是没懂引力波。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021205540GQObno4fehmHAPz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><b>2. 又来了一种支付方式 Apple Pay。</b></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151107XjMAD8RiL2vmN69t.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56289308\" data-format=\"gif\"></figure><p><b>3. 手贱更新了 APP，又想回老版本的时候……</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120554DJr2OGj61hQwqa7L.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 出现了 Sunshine 和 Love-wings 两个（毫无颜值的）国内少女组合。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120555lisMpJ6RyHOP51hQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93160377\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 明星新绯闻。<br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120555jF7BP8ZTAtH3x9GM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62381853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6. 大年三十，求敬业福的铺天盖地。@   A！\r\n  <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120556O3n8psZHR4xLcyED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51055409\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 本来等着吐槽春晚，连吐槽都无力。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021205564SR0Qo9vqDCAl21G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>8. 从大年初一突然到大年初六的时候。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120557RkHdl7rgAQmKTWiC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>9. 要开学了？！！！ @南非籍  </b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021205576524XRs1l3SVmzat.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b></div>\n<p><b>10. （非学生党）再放七天长假要到十一。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120558vMSHNR2niqbcW4zB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>11. 看到新闻里的平均工资的时候。 @夜舸_    <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120558pgNTC3f1ZO0coW2I.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>12. 新同事都是 94、95 后。 <br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021205599t15VN0sB2MjrnFW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>13. 00 年的孩子已经谈恋爱了。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120600XfMRczigKke3Ld6s.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>14. 小学同学的孩子已经上小学。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120600fls3p0XCM5DtRE2h.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>15. 大家都在看“污剧”“雷剧”而我看康熙王朝红高粱的时候。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120601GOFYEBUHvpdzN8w3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. （不腐的人）第一次看到同人文的时候。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021206026veR5GN3JEsIQyjt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>17. 最近有部国产 BL 网剧叫做《上瘾》。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120602lU0qW4k5JNhOeGzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 每次出现新的网络红人。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120602ZPaM9NyXl14tmT5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>19. 买股票的时候。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120603C2gUuTMsynakmKj9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 老家各种小吃的新价格。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120604K41vr7pPodqMx0BW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74698795\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 出国留学一年后再次回到国内的我。 @董泰麟 Wizard</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120605damPKIrfl1nTW4J0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73343606\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. 三天没有刷朋友圈微博新闻 app 的我。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120605awHdfLzJBrPpMIt7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>23. 三天没有更新表情包的我。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120606MU2g9CuXIyzeE5k4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">动图来自：<a href=\"http://giphy.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Giphy</a><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">标题那句话来自崔健的歌《新长征路上的摇滚》。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em>  <br></p>\n\n\n\n"}